      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "use this in order to make templates works (I'll work on an automated msb later):\nservice:\n  name: ve-vnfm-adapter\n  type: NodePort\n  annotations:\n    msb.onap.org/service-info: '[\n      {\n          \"serviceName\": \"{{ include \"common.servicename\" . }}\",\n          \"version\": \"v1\",\n          \"url\": \"/so/ve-vnfm-adapter/v1\",\n          \"protocol\": \"REST\",\n          \"port\": \"{{.Values.service.externalPort}}\",\n          \"visualRange\":\"1\"\n      }\n      ]'\n  ports:\n    - name: https\n      port: 9098\n      nodePort: 09",
      "author": {
