      "file_path": "kubernetes/so/charts/so-ve-vnfm-adapter/resources/config/overrides/override.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 19,
      "message": "As far as I'm aware, this service is to be accessed from externally deployed entities.\n\nBecause of it, I think you should define endpoint to be either local (as Sylvain said), external (using MSB URI) or external without MSB (using NodePort, as we're not there yet to use ingress, I think?) depending on other variables(msbDisabled)/actual use(local/external).",
